snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Xbox One Exclusive DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
Xbox One EXCLUSIVE Downloadable Content is coming to Slime Rancher... for free!

Use the new DLC Playset to dress up your slimes as sea-faring pirates hunting for treasure! Install the XB1-exclusive Emerald Chroma Pack to give your ranch house, vacpack, and ranch tech a shiny, new paint job!

Coming soon to Xbox One!

The physical retail edition for Xbox One and PS4 will be in stores this September. Sign up for our newsletter for more information on when it will release! http://eepurl.com/dnL0cT

Developed by Monomi Park
http://www.slimerancher.com
http://www.monomipark.com
